snippet: An article yesterday about efforts by the United Farm Workers of America to unionize strawberry workers in California misstated the value of the nation's annual strawberry crop. It is $600 million, not $600 billion....
lead_paragraph: An article yesterday about efforts by the United Farm Workers of America to unionize strawberry workers in California misstated the value of the nation's annual strawberry crop. It is $600 million, not $600 billion.
abstract: Correction of May 28 article on efforts to unionize strawberry workers in California, which misstated value of strawberry crop
